talking about the ship that just crashed, I am talking about one that
crashed almost a decade ago, the one that is the reason why we have
this new Beast Wars.&quot;

ELDER gestured broadly, &quot;You see, when that first ship crashed, all
the gaurds were killed and it took reinforcements from Cybertron to
bring at least most of them to justice.&quot; There was a sad look on
ELDER&#39;s face, &quot;But it also started a colonization of Earth. Maximals
and even Predacons came to Earth.&quot;

Frowning again ELDER looked at POLAR CLAW who nodded back.

&quot;You see.&quot; LORD ELDER continued, &quot;It was at this point that somehow
Megatron arrived, and of course Optimus Primal and all the rest. But
what we didn&#39;t know at that time was that Unicron also had his own
minions here on Earth&#39;s moon, assigned to watch the Earth and wait for
a time to attack. And with the arrival of all these . . . &quot; ELDER
waved his hand in the air dissmissively, &quot; . . . colonists, they awoke
and the Beast War began in earnest as now the Earth had a bold new
enemy and we had a war now on three fronts.&quot;

Crossing his arms over his chest he began to pace, &quot;That was when my
job became more important than ever.&quot;

